{"id":105501,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iwan_Roberts","text":"Iwan Wyn Roberts (born 26 June, 1968 in Bangor, Wales) is a Welsh football player. He played for the Welsh national team and several English teams, including Norwich City F.C. and Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C..\nAt Norwich, Roberts twice won the \"player of the year\" trophy.\nAs a player, Roberts was a striker.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"26_June","surface_form":"26 June","offset":23},{"uri":"1968","surface_form":"1968","offset":32},{"uri":"Bangor%2C_Gwynedd","surface_form":"Bangor","offset":40},{"uri":"Wales","surface_form":"Wales","offset":48},{"uri":"Wales","surface_form":"Welsh","offset":60},{"uri":"Association_football","surface_form":"football","offset":66},{"uri":"Wales_national_football_team","surface_form":"Welsh national team","offset":101},{"uri":"England","surface_form":"English","offset":133},{"uri":"Norwich_City_F.C.","surface_form":"Norwich City F.C.","offset":158},{"uri":"Wolverhampton_Wanderers_F.C.","surface_form":"Wolverhampton Wanderers F.C.","offset":180},{"uri":"Trophy","surface_form":"trophy","offset":265},{"uri":"Striker","surface_form":"striker","offset":300}]}